# OpenCode Go API key.
#
# Preferred:
#   ocw bridge key set --stdin
#
# That stores the key once for every project. Use this project-local file only
# when this repo intentionally needs an override.
#
# Project override options:

# Option 1: Plain key (recommended for most users)
# OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY=sk-...

# Option 2: Leave this file empty and export OPENCODE_GO_API_KEY in your shell
# before starting the proxy.
